c: 2
v: 133
t: "Or, were you witness when death appeared before Yaqoub (Jacob)? \"Look\", he said to his sons: \"What will you worship after me?\" They said: \"We shall worship your Allah and the Allah of your fathers— Of Ibrahim (Abraham), Ismail (Ishmael), and Ishaq (Isaac), the One (True) Allah: To Him we bow (in Islam)"